                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/panluan/">潘乱</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2011-07-30</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">我看商君书才是对中国有最深远影响的书，两千多年政经军法几乎都是照本宣科。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

